name: black tie service (variant 1)
description:
This is an example of when working on multiple programs makes planning interesting.

The background is adaptation of a tutorial sketch for the WebGL shader library.

The foreground was generated with CLIP guided Diffusion using stock images which were heavily modified by the program (a Neanderthal skull wearing a top hat instead of H sapiens (sapiens). I then drew over the top using an XP-PEN and GIMP and did some color adjustments.
